data.description: Beautiful move-in ready and well maintained home located just minutes from town, shopping, and schools (Door Dash delivery friendly). The home has two bedrooms on the main floor with a full bathroom, washer/dryer connections, spacious Livingroom, and beautiful kitchen with extra cabinets. The kitchen door opens to the covered front porch, deck and pool.  The lower level features 2 storage closets and two large rooms perfect for an office, craft room, bedroom, or rec room. The lower level can be accessed from the foyer as well as from the carport on the lower level. The large front yard is perfect for outdoor activities and the driveway with carport offers plenty of parking. The newer back deck is partially covered for your grilling needs. The large backyard is great for entertaining or playing outdoor games and has a large swimming pool which makes this home a must have for the hot summer months!
